## 11. Notification Preference Centre (Phase 2)

In Phase 2, clients and consultants will be able to manage their notification preferences from within the portal:

- Toggle individual notification categories on/off (e.g. task updates, billing reminders)
- Choose digest frequency for non-urgent notifications (immediate / daily / weekly)
- Unsubscribe from non-essential emails without unsubscribing from account-critical ones (password reset, billing alerts are always sent)

Preferences will be stored in a `notification_preferences` table in Supabase and checked before each send.

