## 13. Phased Rollout

### Phase 1 — Critical Path (Launch Blockers)
AUTH-01 through AUTH-06, ONB-01, ONB-03, BILL-01 through BILL-04, BILL-07, ADMIN-01 through ADMIN-03

### Phase 2 — Full Operational Coverage
All PROJ-xx, MSG-xx, CON-xx, and remaining BILL-xx and ONB-xx notifications

### Phase 3 — Intelligence & Preferences
Notification preference centre, digest emails, win-back sequences, weekly admin digest

